name: MySQL5
queryCode:
SELECT
	t1.`ACL`,
	t1.`ADDEDBY`,
	t1.`ADDEDDATE`,
	t1.`DELETED`,
	'doc' AS `DOCQTYPE`,
	t1.`EDITEDBY`,
	t1.`EDITEDDATE`,
	t1.`GROUPS`,
	t1.`ID`,
	1 AS `ISFAVOURITES`,
	t1.`KEYWORDS`,
	t1.`LIB`,
	t1.`MODULE`,
	t1.`PRODUCT`,
	t1.`PROJECT`,
	t1.`TITLE`,
	t1.`TYPE`,
	t1.`VERSION`,
	t1.`VIEWS` ,
        t1.docsn
FROM
	`zt_doc` t1
